Table 17.  Police protection sworn and nonsworn employment, payrolls, and percent distribution
of full-time equivalent (FTE) employment of 49 large city governments, October 1995
Note:  Payroll data shown here may not sum to equal police protection October payroll data in table 16 due to rounding.
The October 1995 employment and payrolls data were used for both
1995 and 1996 Justice Expenditure and Employment Extracts.
Jurisdictions without data did not report for 1995.
